section [on the ability of the energy supplier to obtain financing for the renewable energy
generation project that produces the energy that the State is contracting to procure]; AND
– 98 –

WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 353
(II) THE TERMINATION FOR CONVENIENCE CLAUSE
REQUIREMENT UNDER § 13–218(A)(2) OF THIS SUBTITLE.
