(2) (I) A COUNTY OR MUNICIPALITY SHALL:
1. COMPLETE A REMOTE OR IN–PERSON INSPECTION
REQUIRED FOR A PROJECT PERMITTED BY SOLAR PERMITTING SOFTWARE WITHIN
