COUNTY OR MUNICIPALITY SHALL MAKE AVAILABLE AN OPTION FOR REMOTE
INSPECTION THAT IS CAPABLE OF PROVIDING INSPECTION WITHIN 5 BUSINESS DAYS
AFTER RECEIPT OF A REQUEST FOR AN IN–PERSON INSPECTION.
