IN ACCORDANCE WITH THIS SECTION MAY REQUIRE THIRD–PARTY CERTIFICATION
THAT THE PROJECT HAS BEEN INSTALLED IN ACCORDANCE WITH APPLICABLE
STATE AND LOCAL CODES.
(3) A COUNTY OR MUNICIPALITY WITH AUTHORITY OVER
PERMITTING A RESIDENTIAL SOLAR ENERGY SYSTEM MAY PERFORM, AT THE
