(I) IF REMOTE INSPECTION IS UNABLE TO BE COMPLETED;
– 154 –

WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 353
(II) ON REQUEST OR CONCERN OF AN INSPECTOR;
(III) IF SUFFICIENT DATA IS NOT AVAILABLE TO EVALUATE THE
PERMIT APPLICATION; OR
