Ch. 353 2026 LAWS OF MARYLAND
(II) EXCEPT AS PROVIDED IN SUBPARAGRAPH (III) OF THIS
PARAGRAPH, BEGINNING AUGUST 1, 2027, A COUNTY OR MUNICIPALITY MAY NOT
