this subtitle shall provide the technical staff of the Commission, the Office of People’s
Counsel, the Maryland Energy Administration, and the Department of the Environment
with any additional information regarding its plan, as requested.
(c) (1) (i) If directed by the Commission in 2024, and on or before
September 1 every 3 years, starting in 2026, each electric company [and each gas company]
subject to § 7–222(a) of this subtitle that submitted a plan for achieving electricity savings
