REGISTRATION UNDER THIS SECTION.
(C) (1) ON OR BEFORE JANUARY 1, 2027, THE COMMISSION, BY ORDER
OR REGULATION, SHALL ESTABLISH A PROCESS TO REGISTER LARGE LOAD
CUSTOMERS.
(2) THE REGISTRATION PROCESS ESTABLISHED BY THE COMMISSION
SHALL:
(I) APPLY TO NEW OR EXPANDED INTERCONNECTION OF LARGE
LOAD CUSTOMERS;
(II) REQUIRE A LARGE LOAD CUSTOMER TO DISCLOSE TO THE
COMMISSION:
1. WHETHER THE CUSTOMER IS PURSUING A
SUBSTANTIALLY SIMILAR INTERCONNECTION REQUEST WITH THE SAME ELECTRIC
