establishes, if there are insufficient zero–emission credits available to satisfy the electric
companies’ zero–emission credit purchase obligations, the overpayment shall be distributed
to electric companies to be refunded or credited to each distribution customer based on the
customer’s consumption of electricity supply that is subject to the renewable energy
portfolio standard.
